    public class TestGroupByRewriter
extends TestCase2
    Test suite for GroupByRewriter.

    Note: This test suite is actually written at the GroupByRewriter.rewrite(IValueExpression, IVariableFactory, LinkedHashMap) and GroupByRewriter.rewrite(IConstraint, IVariableFactory, LinkedHashMap) level (those are static methods). This is good, but we do not have unit tests at the GroupByRewriter level.
